version_description: Complete chords and lyrics / voicings for special chords / https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gzGVbUGj7sg.

This version is different because the others do not include the entire song, and this one shows chord progression throughout. Also, the chords are simplified and made as easy as possible to play while still being correct.
This an easier version for beginners.
From the One Love concert. Justin plays F, C, G, Am shapes tuned down a half step. Since you are probably in standard these are the chords you need to play along.
